quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  50,36,"∆äuu…óii e gire …óen Min kalki ado ma…ì…ìe, ko …ìeen …ìurnoo…ìe doole, …ìeen mbanngorii e leydi ndiin, ndaarugol taw si …ìe ke…ìay laaworde."
  50,37,"Pellet, woni e …óuum, waajo wonan'de kala jom …ìernde, maa tu…óu…óo noppi hara ko tawaa…óo."
  50,38,"Goo≈ã…óii Min tagii kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, ndeer bal…óe jeegoo, tampere woo he…ìaani Min."
  50,39,"Mu√±√±o e ko …ìe kaalata kon, subbunhinano…óaa Joomi maa ado pu…óal na'ange ngen e ado mutal ngal."
  50,40,"Jemma on kadi, subbunhinano…óaa mo e ka battane [julu…óe] farlaa…óe."
  50,41,"He…óo, √±ande noddoowo o noddoyta e nokkuure …ìattiinde,"
  50,42,"√±ande …ìe naniroyta ha'acaango ngon e hoore goonga. Ko ndeen woni √ëande yaltugol ngol [ka genaale]."
  50,43,"Pellet, ko Monen nguurnata Min mbara, ko ka amen kadi woni ruttorde nde."
  50,44,"√ëalnde leydi ndiin seekotoo […ìe njaltira] ke√±agol; ko nde woni moo…ìirde newaniinde Min."
  50,45,"Ko Minen …ìuri anndude ko …ìe kaalata kon. A wonaa dooloowo…ìe. Haray waajor Alqur'aanaare nden, kala kuloowo kammbaa an on."
  51,1,"Mi woo…óndirii keneeli jaroray…ói (leydi) jaragol !"
  51,2,"Mi woo…óndirii duule donndotoo…óe to…ìo tii…óngo !"
  51,3,"Mi woo…óndirii laa…óe dogiray…óe newaare !"
  51,4,"E peccooji e yamiraande."
  51,5,"ko podete …óon ko, ko …óum goongo."
  51,6,"Haasbeede ko ko wonata.(e goonga)."